subSubSection.paragraph:
The species epithet refers (as a noun in apposition) to the ‘Isabella’ colouration (sensu 
Ridgeway, 1912
) of the dorsal fur of this bat, and also recalls the name of Jan Decher’s daughter Isabelle.

